                            >
                                SR-XXXXX
                            </p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-10 font-mono text-[10px] uppercase">
                            <div class="space-y-1">
                                <p class="opacity-30">Cromatismo</p>
                                <p id="user-hex" class="font-bold text-lg">#FFFFFF</p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="space-y-1">
